---
const { t } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="cycle">
	<div class="title">
		<h2 class="aos aos-fadeIn"><span>不只是一次合作</span>而是一場能持續十年、二十年的循環。</h2>
		<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Cycle.svg" alt="" id="cycle-img" />
		<!-- mobile Text -->
		<div class="mobileCycleText">
			<div class="title-with-arrow">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="23" height="19" viewBox="0 0 23 19" fill="none">
					<path
						d="M2 10.4998C6.33333 9.8331 16.1 8.69976 20.5 9.49976C21.1005 9.60895 21.3066 9.60164 21.5 9.5M13 2C16.7419 4.44657 21.5 9.5 21.5 9.5M21.5 9.5C20.6095 10.6667 18.6 13.8 17 17"
						stroke="#00D959"
						stroke-width="3"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
				</svg>
				<h3 class="emfont-XiaoLai">發覺新秀</h3>
			</div>
			<p>舉辦年會、黑客松，提供各領域人才展現自我與交流所學的舞台。</p>

			<div class="title-with-arrow">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="23" height="19" viewBox="0 0 23 19" fill="none">
					<path
						d="M2 10.4998C6.33333 9.8331 16.1 8.69976 20.5 9.49976C21.1005 9.60895 21.3066 9.60164 21.5 9.5M13 2C16.7419 4.44657 21.5 9.5 21.5 9.5M21.5 9.5C20.6095 10.6667 18.6 13.8 17 17"
						stroke="#00D959"
						stroke-width="3"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
				</svg>
				<h3 class="emfont-XiaoLai">培育人才</h3>
			</div>
			<p>推動教育公平、促進產學交流，培養組織與領導能力</p>

			<div class="title-with-arrow">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="23" height="19" viewBox="0 0 23 19" fill="none">
					<path
						d="M2 10.4998C6.33333 9.8331 16.1 8.69976 20.5 9.49976C21.1005 9.60895 21.3066 9.60164 21.5 9.5M13 2C16.7419 4.44657 21.5 9.5 21.5 9.5M21.5 9.5C20.6095 10.6667 18.6 13.8 17 17"
						stroke="#00D959"
						stroke-width="3"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
				</svg>
				<h3 class="emfont-XiaoLai">創造影響</h3>
			</div>
			<p>尋找使用者與徵才，搶佔年輕開發者的心</p>
		</div>

		<p class="slogan">
			參與 SITCON 不只是曝光，而是成為社群的一部分。<br />從第一場 SITCON 到第一個專案團隊，企業與人才的故事由你啟動。
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="sdgs">
		<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" />
		<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" />
		<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" />
		<img src="/cfs/Cycle/Hungry.svg" alt="" />
	</div>
	<div class="sdgs-text">
		<h4>消除飢餓</h4>
		<p>開會前後或沒事會揪團去吃好吃的。</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	section {
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	#cycle-img {
		display: block;
		margin: auto;
	}
	.mobileCycleText {
		display: none;
		max-width: 35rem;
		margin: auto;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	span {
		display: block;
	}

	.mobileCycleText .title-with-arrow {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.mobileCycleText svg {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.mobileCycleText h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}
	.mobileCycleText p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.slogan {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.sdgs {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.sdgs-text {
		max-width: 20rem;
		margin: 2rem auto;
	}

	.sdgs img {
		width: 8rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 50rem) {
		#cycle-img {
			content: url("/cfs/Cycle/mobileCycle.svg");
			width: 70%;
			height: auto;
		}

		.mobileCycleText {
			display: block;
		}
	}
</style>
